<div class="midascontainer"><h1>Midas&reg; Rewards Program Offered by Ricktag&reg; <br/>Network Solutions Inc.</h1>
<h3>Terms and Conditions</h3>

<h2>Program Overview</h2>
<ol style="padding-left: 10px;">
<li>The Midas&reg;Rewards Program (the "Program") is a loyalty reward program offered by Ricktag&reg; Network Solutions Inc. ("Ricktag", "us", "our" or "we") to customers of Midas (the "Stores" or each individually a "Store") and online at <a href="www.ricktag.ca/midas">www.ricktag.ca/midas</a>.

1. The Program allows persons who have completed the membership enrolment steps in accordance with the present Terms and Conditions and who have been issued a Midas Rewards Card (the "Program Members" or "Members") to collect Midas points when making purchases in-stores on items identified from time to time by Midas ("Eligible Purchases"), and to redeem these Midas Points for rewards, benefits and/or rebates offered by Midas and Ricktag Merchant Partners.

Ricktag may designate from time to time, Merchant Partners from whom Members will be able to collect or redeem Ricktag Points in the Program (the "Program Partners" or "Partners").

Members acquire no vested right or entitlement to the continued availability of any particular reward or benefit, Program Partner or redemption level.</li>
<h2>Participation in the Program</h2>
<h2>Membership Enrolment</h2>


<li>Membership is free and no initial purchase is required in order to become a Member.</li>
<li>To enroll, you must have a valid Canadian address and be 16 years of age or older. At a minimum, you must provide your first name, last name, and a valid email address. If you do not have a valid email address, you must provide a valid mailing address and phone number. You may also be asked to provide data such as gender or preferred language during the sign-up process. Only one Midas rewards account ("Midas Rewards Account" or "Account") is permitted per person.</li>
<li>Only one loyalty program account (i.e. one Midas Rewards Account) is permitted per person</li>
<li>To become a Member, simply ask a Store employee to sign you up or visit <a href="www.ricktag.ca/midas">www.ricktag.ca/midas</a> and complete the online form. To become a valid Member, you must complete the enrolment process by providing complete and accurate information and indicating your acceptance of these Terms and Conditions. You may be required to register your account to complete the enrolment process within a defined period of time before Midas Points are awarded to your Account.</li>
<li>After completion, you will receive a Midas rewards member number ("Member Number"). If you sign up in-store, you will be given a card with a unique Member Number (the "Midas Rewards Card" or the "Card"). </li>
<li>The Midas Rewards Card is not a credit card. The Card is the property of Ricktag and it may be revoked at any time by Ricktag in the event of breach of the Terms and Conditions of the Program by a Member, misuse or abuse of the Program by a Member, fraud, and/or any other actions deemed by Ricktag to be contrary to the Program or the interests of its Members or Partners.</li>
<li>Members cannot share their account number and account information with anyone else. Membership benefits apply only to the individual Midas Rewards Account holder. Account information, including, but not limited to, the Midas Rewards Account password should be protected and kept secure.</li>
<li>You must advise us immediately of any changes of Personal Information (as defined herein) including name, address, and e-mail address either by visiting <a href="www.ricktag.ca/midas">www.ricktag.ca/midas</a> or emailing us at customerservice@ricktag.ca. Ricktag shall not be liable for misdirected email or mail communications, including any notices under these Terms and Conditions or any consequences thereof where your Personal Information is inaccurate or no longer valid. If we believe that some of our records are inaccurate, we may contact you to verify our records. We reserve the right to cancel any Account for which we have incomplete or inaccurate Personal Information and all points redemptions on that Account may be blocked and any points awarded may be forfeited. The submission of false or fictitious Personal Information will result in all the Midas Points accumulated on an Account being forfeited.</li>
<li>Midas reserves the right to refuse issuance of an Account to any person who does not follow the prescribed enrolment procedures.</li>
<li>Midas rewards membership is only available to individuals. Midas rewards membership will not be available to corporations, businesses, charities, partnerships, enterprises, schools or anyone other than an individual, unless written approval is received in advance from Midas, in its sole discretion. Midas Points will not be awarded if in Midas's reasonable opinion the merchandise purchased will be used for resale or commercial use and any Midas Points awarded on such purchases will be forfeited. If a Midas rewards Member was awarded points for an offer or promotion in which a Member purchased product in excess of reasonable quantities, the Midas Points awarded as a result of that offer or promotion may be forfeited without prior notice and the Account may be suspended or closed.</li>
<li>If for any reason we believe a Member is under the age of 16, we reserve the right to request proof of age. If such proof is not provided, all Personal Information regarding that individual may be deleted from our system and the Membership may be terminated, including the immediate forfeiture of all Midas points.</li>


<h2>Collection of plum Points</h2>


<li>To collect Midas Points following enrolment, you must make Eligible Purchases in-store by presenting your personal valid Midas Rewards Card. Any unauthorized reproduction of the Midas Rewards Card may lead to legal prosecution and forfeiture of all Midas Points and membership in the Program.<br/>
<strong>At Cash, In-store</strong>: The Member's personal Midas Rewards Card must be presented to the cashier before the Eligible Purchase transaction is completed.</li>
<li><strong>Online:</strong>  Midas Points will not be issued for every dollar spent online. However, from time to time, bonus Midas Points may be awarded for purchases made online, as advertised by Ricktag on <a href="www.ricktag.ca/midas">www.ricktag.ca/midas</a> and/or in-stores. Also, Members can be, from time to time, eligible to receive a "Member Discount" on any participating Ricktag Merchants, as advertised by Ricktag from time to time at http://<a href="www.ricktag.ca/midas">www.ricktag.ca/midas</a></li>
<li>Midas Points may be awarded retroactively if the original receipt and your Midas Rewards Card is produced in-stores within 14 days of the date of the original Eligible Purchase.</li>
<li>Midas Points will be awarded at the rate of 5% Midas Points for each dollar spent on Eligible Purchases. Midas Points will be calculated by reference to the net (Eligible Purchase price less discounts) pre-tax total on each cash register receipt. Midas may offer special promotions from time to time offering additional Midas Points("bonus Midas points"). Such bonus Midas points, once awarded, shall form part of the Member's Midas Points balance (the Midas Points and bonus Midas Points collectively referred to as "Midas Points").</li>
<li>All Midas Points awarded for an Eligible Purchase as well as the Member's current Midas Points balance can be found in you're My Account page at <a href="www.ricktag.ca/midas">www.ricktag.ca/midas</a>. In the event of a discrepancy our internal database and records will govern.<br /><br />
Occasionally, through specified promotions by participating Stores and/or Program Partners, additional Midas Points(and/or other rewards or benefits) may be awarded for using the Midas Rewards Card, or for being a Member.
</li>
<li>Midas's standard Return/Exchange Policy applies. In the event of a return/exchange of any Eligible Purchase, Midas Points will be deducted automatically from the Account that was used for the Eligible Purchase (whether or not the Midas Rewards Card is presented at the time of return and/or exchange). </li>
<li>All Midas Points totals, will be deemed correct unless otherwise substantiated by the Member by bringing forward evidence satisfactory to Midas. In the case of a discrepancy, our internal database and records govern. Discrepancies must be addressed with the Ricktag Customer Service Centre within three months of the date on which the discrepancy occurred. Midas reserves the right to restrict redemption or put a "hold" on Midas Points for up to 90 days from the date the points are posted to an Account if Ricktag has reasonable belief that fraud has occurred or in the event of a breach or suspected breach of the Terms and Conditions of this Program.</li>
<li>Midas Points are not transferable from one Member to another. Midas may, however, in its sole discretion allow the transfer of Midas Points in accordance with the "transfer points" terms and conditions posted from time to time at <a href="www.ricktag.ca/midas">www.ricktag.ca/midas</a></li>
<li>Midas Points are reduced to zero upon closure of a Midas rewards membership.</li>
<li>Upon the death of a Member, the Member's account will be closed and any Midas Points in the account will be forfeited. Midas Points are not divisible in the case of divorce.</li>
<li>Should any Member not collect Midas Points using a Midas Rewards Card or redeem Midas Points for 14 consecutive calendar months, the membership will be deemed to be inactive and all accumulated Midas Points will be forfeited. If a Member's only activity in 14 consecutive calendar months consists of transferring points under any Midas promotion in existence from time to time, the membership will be deemed inactive and all accumulated Midas Points will be forfeited.</li>

<h2>Redemption of Points</h2>

<li>(a) Midas Points may be redeemed for rewards consisting of a predetermined dollar discount reward off a purchase in-store, in accordance with the Midas Points redemption schedule in force on the date when the Midas Points are redeemed by the Member ("Redemption Transaction"). <br />
The following redemption schedule is provided for illustrative purposes only. The updated Midas Points redemption schedule in effect from time to time is available at <a href="www.ricktag.ca/midas">www.ricktag.ca/midas</a><br /><br />
