<br /><br />
Points will not be awarded on the portion of the Redemption Transaction paid for by redemption of Midas points. From time to time, special promotions may be run during which one or more redemption level(s) may temporarily be altered and/or suspended, new redemption levels added or points may be redeemed directly towards the purchase of specific products or services. Promotions may vary from Store to Store and online.
(b) Ricktag may, from time to time, offer supplementary programs, rewards, benefits or promotions related to the Midas rewards program. 
</li>
<li>In accordance with Federal and Provincial tax legislation, GST, PST, HST and any other applicable taxes are calculated and payable by the Member on the full amount of the purchase price of the item subject to a dollar discount reward during a Redemption Transaction.</li>
<li>Subject to section 29, a Member's Midas Points balance will be reduced by the number of points required to obtain the desired point redemption level. Unredeemed Midas Points plus any Midas Points awarded in the current Redemption Transaction will remain in the Member's Midas Rewards Account and can be applied to a subsequent Redemption Transaction</li>
<li>Midas Points can only be redeemed if the required point redemption level is acquired prior to the Redemption Transaction. A Member may not make more than two redemptions, at any reward level, within one day. Only one redemption is available per Redemption Transaction.</li>
<li>When redeeming Midas points, Midas will automatically select the maximum eligible Midas Points redemption level available. Alternatively, you may select a different eligible redemption level by informing the cashier prior to the Redemption Transaction. In either case, your Account must have the appropriate number of Midas points. For example, if you have accumulated 45,000 Midas points, the maximum redemption level available is 25,000 Midas Points(based on the example redemption schedule referenced above). However, you may elect to redeem only 10,000 points on a $170.00 transaction; in this case the reduction off the purchase price will be $70.00.</li>
<li>If the purchase price is lower than the redemption value of the points, the remaining dollar value will be forfeited. For example, if you have accumulated 45,000 Midas Points and wish to redeem all these points on a transaction with a purchase price of eligible products of $150.00, then the reduction off the purchase price will be $150.00 and the difference between the $250.00 maximum reward discount and the $150.00 discount (i.e. $100.00) will be forfeited. (This example is based on the example redemption schedule referenced above.)</li>
<li>Products and services eligible for Midas points redemption will be posted at http://<a href="www.ricktag.ca/midas">www.ricktag.ca/midas</a> and updated on a periodic basis. Redemption Transactions can only be made in-store and at cash only. </li>
<li>Midas Points may not be collected or redeemed by any person other than the Midas rewards Member. A Member must present his/her Midas Rewards Card when redeeming Midas Points to protect the integrity of the Member's points balance. Proof of Card ownership may be required. Each Member is responsible to ensure that all Personal Information is correct and up-to-date and Midas reserves the right to block redemptions where the Member information is inaccurate or incomplete. Members are entirely responsible for keeping their Account secure.</li>
<li>You must notify Ricktag immediately if your Midas Rewards Card is lost or stolen. Contact us at 1-800-560-4135 to ensure a replacement card is properly issued to the correct person, and that all Midas Points in your Account are accessible only by you. Upon verification of proper identification, a new Member number or Card will be provided to the Member by the Ricktag Customer Service Centre or in-store, respectively. The accumulated unredeemed Midas Points balance shall remain intact.</li>
<li>If a lost Midas Rewards Card is found and used by any other person, all Midas Points relating to purchases made by such other person will be credited to the Member's Account. Midas assumes no liability or responsibility for Midas Points redeemed by any person(s) prior to the notification to the Ricktag Customer Service Centre that the Midas Rewards Card is lost or stolen. Any Midas Points redeemed prior to notification shall be at the Member's risk.</li>
<li>Ricktag will not be liable or responsible in any manner for any tax consequences or any charge imposed by or with the authority of any government, which may flow from any participation in the Midas Rewards Program.</li>
<li>From time to time, Ricktag may advertise or offer exclusive offers to select Members to redeem Midas Points for items other than a discount reward, or receive other benefits or discounts.</li>
<li>Midas Points have no cash value and are not exchangeable for cash. Except as permitted from time to time by Midas at <a href="www.ricktag.ca/midas">www.ricktag.ca/midas</a>, Midas Points cannot be assigned, exchanged, sold, traded, bartered, purchased or given by gift or otherwise sold. Any Midas Points so acquired are void. The accumulation of Midas Points does not entitle the Program Members to any vested rights, and Midas and/or the Program Partners do not guarantee in any way the continued availability of any reward, redemption level, rebate or any other benefit. Ricktag assumes no liability to Members as regards the addition or deletion of Program Partners or of items for which Midas Points can be collected and/or redeemed.</li>
<li>In the event of a "Sale" of the Midas franchise that enrolled you into the Midas Rewards Program, Program Members will be notified by email or by mail and be given 60 days to redeem their Midas Points in-store or the members points will be forfeited.</li>

<h2>Gift Cards</h2>
<li>For all purchased gift cards, card holders will have 12 calendar months to use the full value of the card. After the 12 months is up, a $5/month service fee will apply until the value on card totals $0.00.</li>
<li>Promotional gift cards have no true cash value and are used as a promotional device and it is up to the Midas owner to honor them. </li>
<li>In the event of a "Sale" of the Midas franchise that enrolled you into the Midas Rewards Program, it is up to the new owner to continue to honor the promotional gift cards.</li>

<h2>Privacy</h2>
<li>We are committed to protecting your privacy. We will maintain the privacy and security of all personal information collected from Members, including, but not limited to: name, address, email address, telephone numbers, date of birth, account number and purchasing information ("Personal Information").<br/><br/>

We collect your Personal Information for the following purposes:<br /><br />
<ul>
<li>To set up and administer the Program including ongoing management of Midas Accounts, and to accurately record points and to update point balances;</li>
<li>To process redemptions and issue rewards;</li>
<li>To communicate with Members;</li>
<li>To send Members a Notice of Termination in compliance with the present Terms and Conditions</li>
<li>To understand Members' shopping and information needs and preferences, and to offer Members relevant information, products, services and rewards to meet those needs and interests; and to provide Members with special offers and rewards from Midas and the Program Partners. </li>


</ul>
 
By providing your Personal Information to us, you consent to our use of the information for the purposes specified herein.</li>
<li>On occasion Ricktag may collect additional personal information from Members on a voluntary basis through questionnaires or other methods. The Midas Rewards membership status of any Member who does not wish to participate will not be affected.</li>
<li>All membership information will be used solely by Ricktag and will not be sold or rented to any other organization. Personal Information will not be used or disclosed for purposes other than those for which it was collected, except with your consent or as required by law.</li>
<li>You have the right to know what information is held in your Member file and the right to challenge the accuracy and completeness of your information and have it amended as appropriate. To request access to your file, a written request should be sent to:
<div class="midasitems">
	Ricktag Networks Solutions Inc.<br />
	60 Wood Cres<br />
	Bradford, Ontario L3Z 2G2<br /> 
	M5V 1L8<br />
	email: <a href="mailto:customerservice@ricktag.ca">customerservice@ricktag.ca </a><br/>
	1.800.560.4135<br/>
</div>
</li>
<li>Member information is stored in Ricktag's confidential databases located in Bradford. Access to this information will be restricted only to authorized personnel of Ricktag, its agents or Partners for the purpose of carrying out the Program.</li>
<li>On occasion Ricktag may communicate special offers, information and services to Ricktag Rewards Members. Any Member who does not wish to receive these offers may indicate so during the enrolment process. Alternatively, Members may advise us at 1-800-560-4135 or online at <a href="www.ricktag.ca/midas">www.ricktag.ca/midas</a></li>
<li>All Member information will be subject to the Ricktag Network Solutions Inc. Privacy Policy as amended from time to time in accordance with its terms. For the most current version of the Ricktag Network Solutions Inc. Privacy Policy please see <a href="www.ricktag.ca/midas">www.ricktag.ca/midas</a></li>


<h2>General Information</h2>


<li>The Midas Rewards Program will terminate at 11:59 p.m. on April 4, 2013 (the "Termination Date"). At 12:00 a.m. on the first day following the Termination Date (the "Renewal Date"), the Program will be renewed automatically for successive terms of six (6) months following the Renewal Date (the "Renewed Termination Date") and the Member's Midas Points will be maintained unless: <br /><br />

	<ol>
		<li>Ricktag gives notice by e-mail or regular mail to the Program Members, at least thirty (30) days before the Termination Date or the Renewed Termination Date, that the Midas Rewards Program will not be renewed ("Notice of Termination"). In this case, all Midas Points collected by Members will be redeemable for a minimum of sixty (60) days after the Termination Date or the Renewed Termination Date, as the case may be; OR</li>
		<li> The Member notifies Midas that it no longer wishes to be a Member. A Member may notify Midas by email at <a href="mailto:customerservice@ricktag.ca">customerservice@ricktag.ca </a><br/> or by telephone at 1-800-560-4135.</li>
	</ol>

If Ricktag gives a Notice of Termination, it may, in its sole discretion, establish a replacement program.</li>
<li>If events beyond Ricktag's control materially affect Ricktag's ability to operate the Program, the Program may be suspended or terminated without notice.</li>
<li>Your acceptance of the Terms and Conditions on-line and/or first time usage of a Midas Rewards Card constitutes your agreement to all the Terms and Conditions of the Program.</li>
<li>Any abuse by a Member of the Program's privileges, any failure by a Member to follow the Program's Terms and Conditions, or any misrepresentation by a Member may subject the Member to expulsion from the Program, including forfeiture of all accumulated Midas points.</li>
<li>Every effort has been made to ensure that the information herein is correct. Ricktag is not responsible for any errors or omissions in printed copies of these Terms and Conditions nor those published from time to time on its website.</li>
<li>Any waiver by Ricktag of the strict observance, performance or compliance by a Member with any of the Terms and Conditions contained herein, either expressly granted or by course of conduct, shall be effective only in the specific instance and shall not be deemed to be a waiver of any rights or remedies of Midas as a result of any other failure to observe, perform or comply with the Terms and Conditions. No delay or omission by Midas in exercising any right or remedy hereunder shall operate as waiver thereof or of any other right or remedy.</li>
<li> By participating in this Program, you agree that: (i) you will contact us directly and give us the opportunity to try to resolve any and all disputes before you take any action in court, or otherwise; (ii) any and all claims, judgments and awards shall in no event include legal fees; and (iv) under no circumstances will Member be permitted to obtain awards for, and Member hereby waives all rights to claim punitive, incidental and consequential damages and any other damages other than for actual out-of-pocket expenses, and any and all rights to have damages multiplied or otherwise increased.</li>
<li>In the event that any provision in these Terms and Conditions is determined to be invalid, illegal, or unenforceable, such determination shall not affect the validity and enforceability of any other remaining provisions of these Terms and Conditions.</li>
</ol>
